data.chText: 立体声音响（或录音机等）
data.enText: a machine that plays CDs, etc., sometimes with a radio, that has two separate speakers so that you hear different sounds from each

data.chText: 车用 / 个人立体声音响
我们在立体声音响上放点音乐吧。
data.enText: Let's put some music on the stereo.
the system for playing recorded music, speech, etc. in which the sound is directed through two channels

means: 立体声音响(或录音机等)

tr: reproducer in which two microphones feed two or more loudspeakers to give a three-dimensional effect to the sound
two photographs taken from slightly different angles that appear three-dimensional when viewed together
designating sound transmission from two sources through two channels

value.def: Stereo is used to describe a sound system in which the sound is played through two speakers.

example.tran: 具有环绕立体声效果的扩音器

value.def: A stereo is a cassette or CD player with two speakers.
value.tran: 立体声磁带播放机;立体声激光唱片播放机;立体音响

trans: 个人音响(可随身携带的备有耳机的激光唱片或磁带小型放音机)
